{"name":"Water Walk","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Environment</h2><p><em>You take yourself for a stroll across the lake</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You or an ally gain the ability to walk on water as if it were solid ground. If the water is rough or choppy treat it as difficult terrain. The target of this ritual can end its benefits as a free action. The target can immerse itself in water or swim underwater if desired without needing to end the ritual.</p>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Environment","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"SvVFn6k4qMZgeYwO"}
{"name":"Leomund's Instant Camp","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Accommodation</h2><p><em>You spin around three times and voila, your campsite is ready</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When the ritual completes you conjure a campsite with half a dozen tents, a campfire, a latrine, and a clothesline.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Accommodation","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"AaeL4Pllhq1897iT"}
{"name":"Lively Step","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Travel</h2><p><em>You and your party feel energized, like the weight of the world has been taken off your shoulders</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You gather your group in a circle, holding ands and repeating the words of the ritual under your direction. Up to a dozen creatures can be affected by this ritual at a time. While traveling overland by foot you go 25% faster.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Travel","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"15 minutes","duration":"8 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"zgSghLVXLJjlzl4g"}
{"name":"Magic Circle: Beast","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Abjuration</h2><p><em>You immobilize the dangerous animal with magical chains</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You draw a 10-foot-radius circle on the ground which creates a 20-foot-tall cylinder of magical energy. Choose inwards or outwards - the circle has the following effects when a beast or its attacks cross the circle in the chosen direction</p>\n<ul><li>The creature cannot willingly cross the circle boundary by nonmagical means. They must succeed on an Arcana check with a DC equal to your check result to suceed via magical means.</li>\n<li>The creature has disadvantage on attacks that cross the circle boundary.</li>\n<li>Targets of attacks that cross the circle boundary are immune to Charm, Fear, and Possession effects.</li>\n</ul>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Abjuration","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"zbxMw54DaSQjBIYW"}
{"name":"Magic Mouth","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Communication</h2><p><em>You leave some words of warning for whatever party stumbles through next</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You implant a message within an object in range, a message that is uttered when a trigger condition is met. Choose an object that you can see and that isn't being worn or carried by another creature. Then speak the message, which must be 25 words or less, though it can be delivered over as long as 10 minutes. Finally, determine the circumstance that will trigger the ritual to deliver your message.</p>\n<p>When that circumstance occurs, a magical mouth appears on the object and recites the message in your voice and at the same volume you spoke. If the object you chose has a mouth or something that looks like a mouth (for example, the mouth of a statue), the magical mouth appears there so that the words appear to come from the object's mouth. When you cast this ritual, you can have the ritual end after it delivers its message, or it can remain and repeat its message whenever the trigger occurs.</p>\n<p>The triggering circumstance can be as general or as detailed as you like, though it must be based on visual or audible conditions that occur within 30 feet of the object. For example, you could instruct the mouth to speak when any creature moves within 30 feet of the object or when a silver bell rings within 30 feet of it.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Communication","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Until Dispelled"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"xyWBlvVvbRiqjbXb"}
{"name":"Rapid Decomposition","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Restoration</h2><p><em>Sprinkling the dragonshards on the body, it dissappears before your eyes</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You cause a body to disintegrate over the next few minutes, not even leaving a trace that can be used in a Raise Dead ritual. The trace of this ritual can be detected by an Arcana check equal to the Arcana check result of this ritual.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Restoration","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"10 minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"XzB2wuonDKEcqgsx"}
{"name":"Water Breathing","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Travel</h2><p><em>The gnome wizard guarantees that while he still can't swim, he certainly won't drown</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You give a creature with lungs the ability to breathe water for the duration.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Travel","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"OTzHdle7ihxF0Zyh"}
{"name":"Alice's Grow/Shrink Object","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Deception - Polymorph</h2><p><em>With a mix of giant's bread crumbs and newt's juice you manipulate an object's size for a duration</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you cast this ritual, select one object or portion of an object no bigger than a 5' cube. You may change its size to be anywhere from 10 times its current size to 1/10th. The object retains its density, meaning that its weight will change as the extra material is either conjured from or sent to the aether for the duration.</p>\n<p>When the ritual finishes casting or expires, the object gradually changes its size over the course of thirty seconds. This change is accompanied by either the sound of the object inflating or deflating depending on whether the object is growing or shrinking.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Deception - Polymorph","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"6 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"LJYM88SAkhQGmlKj"}
{"name":"Augury","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Divination</h2><p><em>Swirling winds arrange the sticks laid out before you to help decide on your future course of action.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>As you cast the ritual focus on a specific course of action. When you complete the ritual you receive an omen as to whether this is a good <em>(weal)</em> or bad <em>(woe)</em> idea, and a vague sense of what risks may arise.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Divination","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"30 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"9ZCD4wP7hID1iGSY"}
{"name":"Burrowing","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Travel</h2><p><em>You move effortlessly through the earth with just a thought</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You or an ally gain a Burrow Speed of 20', which lets you move up to 20' per move action through loose earth. If the earth is firm you're slowed to 10', and you cannot move through solid rock. As you burrow you leave very loose earth that obscures your path but can be easily moved by a creature without a burrow speed.</p>\n<p>While in the earth you do not have any special sense of direction. If traveling for extended periods of time you can make Survival checks to navigate, with the DC based on your familiarity with the area and the peculiarities of the terrain.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Travel","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"3 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"9YeC5mj6KWjTYof5"}
{"name":"Castar's Invisibility","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Deception - Illusion</h2><p><em>With the final words an ally disappears from view.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>While you cast this ritual, choose yourself or an ally. You turn the target invisible to sight for the duration. If the target attacks another creature or takes damage the invisibility breaks. <em>(Invisibility can also be countered by common items like bags of flour or closed doors)</em></p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Deception - Illusion","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"kzg0C3FUz3Q88iZC"}
{"name":"Dailan's Seeing: Invisibility","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Divination</h2><p><em>What was hidden from view becomes apparent to you</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you cast this ritual, choose yourself or an ally. The target gains the ability to clearly see through invisibility effects that have a lower Arcana check result than the one you made for this ritual, and can see a vague outline of invisibility effects with an Arcana check that is up to 10 higher than yours.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Divination","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"8 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"XeKuk1iExQVq27Aa"}
{"name":"Dispel Magic","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Abjuration</h2><p><em>Ipso Facto Dispello</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You work to undo a permanent piece of magic. To do this you compare your Arcana check result with the Arcana check made to create the piece of magic you're undoing. If your check result is equal to or greater than the one made to create the persistent effect it is dispelled.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Abjuration","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"QjihpnmBe3LPWclB"}
{"name":"Ethereal Mount: Aquatic","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Travel</h2><p><em>A horse with a fish tail bubbles up from the water, ready to venture forth</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you finish casting the ritual, you summon a Water Horse that is absolutely loyal to you. This horse cannot attack, has hit points equal to 20 + 10 x your level, and has your defenses. The horse has a land speed of 20' and a swim speed of 40', and do not need to breathe.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Travel","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"8 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"VT0nfPYaLsmDNhgQ"}
{"name":"Leomund's Instant Meal","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Accommodation</h2><p><em>Just add water!</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You conjure a delicious, filling single course meal to accomodate up to 8 people.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Accommodation","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"5 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"M9xOUMPY4I4GFSPl"}
{"name":"Lighten Armor","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Travel</h2><p><em>Now that your plate armor is unnoticeable, you feel the weight of the world much more intensely.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>As you cast this ritual, select a piece of armor. It no longer imposes an armor check penalty on Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution based skill checks for the duration of the ritual.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Travel","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"4 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"09zyP6NlNdkGPDhl"}
{"name":"Magic Circle: Anima","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Abjuration</h2><p><em>Etched runes surprised the vampire who thought the girl was easy prey, not bait</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You draw a 10-foot-radius circle on the ground which creates a 20-foot-tall cylinder of magical energy. Choose inwards or outwards - the circle has the following effects when a animated creature or its attacks cross the circle in the chosen direction</p>\n<ul><li>The creature cannot willingly cross the circle boundary by nonmagical means. They must succeed on an Arcana check with a DC equal to your check result to suceed via magical means.</li>\n<li>The creature has disadvantage on attacks that cross the circle boundary.</li>\n<li>Targets of attacks that cross the circle boundary are immune to Charm, Fear, and Possession effects.</li>\n</ul>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Abjuration","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"xWYMwQYQzBWWz1eT"}
{"name":"Shadow Puppets","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Creation</h2><p><em>Shadows dance to your tune.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>For the duration of the ritual, you can command shadows to move as you desire. You can stretch or shorten any shadow or even disjoint it from its owner, although no shadow can leave line of sight from its source. If the source of a shadow moves out of line of sight of a disjointed shadow, the shadow instantaneously returns to its source and resumes normal behavior until otherwise commanded.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Creation","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"aSWLQMF35HUc20X4"}
{"name":"Shenta's Helping Hand","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Accommodation</h2><p><em>A glowing yellow hand helps the Ghallanda matriarch in the kitchen as she prepares a traditional 27 course meal.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You conjure a Small <em>(So ~3 feet in height)</em> floating hand that autonomously obeys your commands to the best of its ability. The hand can lift up to 50 lbs. of material. If the hand would travel farther than 100' from you it instantaneously teleports back to you, dropping whatever it was holding. You can redirect the hand's tasks as a free action, although the hand cannot perform attacks. The hand is impervious to incoming attacks, and has a fly speed of 30' (hover).</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Accommodation","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"4 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"vibzt0Em9xRJHImx"}
{"name":"Vylae's Minor Image","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Deception - Illusion</h2><p><em>If it walks like a duck and quacks like a duck... Might just be Vylae's Minor Image.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You create the image of an object, a creature, or some other visible phenomenon that is no larger than a 15-foot cube. The image appears at a spot within range and lasts for the duration. The image can make sounds ranging from a whisper to a roar, but does not smell or have other sensory effects. You can make the sound as dynamic as you desire.</p>\n<p>You can use a standard action to cause the image to move to any spot within range. As the image changes location, you can alter its appearance so that its movements appear natural for the image. For example, if you create an image of a creature and move it, you can alter the image so that it appears to be walking.</p>\n<p>Physical interaction with the image reveals it to be an illusion, because things can pass through it. A creature that uses a standard action to examine the image can determine that it is an illusion with a successful Insight check against your Arcana check result. If a creature discerns the illusion for what it is, the creature can see through the image.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Deception - Illusion","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"VKfCysr277ekyzIy"}
{"name":"Alter Self","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Deception - Polymorp</h2><p><em>Your elven ally grows shorter and shorter as a beard grows out longer and longer</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You alter your or a humanoid ally's physical features to appear as any other kind of humanoid. If you wish to imitate a particular individual you must be familiar with that individual, and your Arcana check result is the Perception DC to discern the difference. As usual, the target's Impress competes against Insight to convince they are not an imposter for direct interactions.</p>\n<p>In addition to physical appearances you can use Alter Self to grant one of the following</p>\n<ul><li>Aquatic Adaptation: The recipient gains the ability to breathe underwater and a swim speed equal to their walking speed</li>\n<li>Natural Weapons: The recipient grows claws, fangs, etc. that they are proficient in, giving them an unarmed melee attack at a +2 proficiency bonus and 1d6 damage.</li>\n</ul>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Deception - Polymorp","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"N31pkiSMWQVAytCp"}
{"name":"Countermoon","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Abjuration</h2><p><em>With 12 moons in the sky this is relevant most of the month</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you begin this ritual, choose a werecreature that is in their animal form within 30 feet of you. If the target stays within range of you throughout the entire casting of the ritual they are forced back into their humanoid form and cannot transform back for the duration of the ritual.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Abjuration","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"BNJamgsVajNDGqHq"}
{"name":"Dailan's Seeing: True Form","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Divination</h2><p><em>Everyone except you is a changeling</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you cast this ritual, choose yourself or an ally. The target gains the ability to see the true form of creatures or objects subject to polymorph effects that have a lower Arcana check result than the one you made for this ritual. You can tell something has been polymorphed if the Arcana check on the effect is up to 10 higher than the one made for this ritual. If a creature is subject to a polymorph effect that did not initially require an Arcana check, they make an Arcana check when the beneficiary of this ritual sees them.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Divination","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"8 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"AHeYvO10O9L9ncDs"}
{"name":"Ethereal Stable","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Travel</h2><p><em>A full herd of horses appears in the livery of your choice</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You summon up to 8 ethereal horses that are absolutely loyal to you in the livery of your choosing. The horses cannot attack and have hit points equal to 20 + 10 per level, and have your defenses. The horses have a speed of 50'.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Travel","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"8 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"9Yu9AdUyhnlgIeyU"}
{"name":"Magic Circle: Humanoid","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Abjuration</h2><p><em>Kinky</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You draw a 10-foot-radius circle on the ground which creates a 20-foot-tall cylinder of magical energy. Choose inwards or outwards - the circle has the following effects when a humanoid or its attacks cross the circle in the chosen direction</p>\n<ul><li>The creature cannot willingly cross the circle boundary by nonmagical means. They must succeed on an Arcana check with a DC equal to your check result to suceed via magical means.</li>\n<li>The creature has disadvantage on attacks that cross the circle boundary.</li>\n<li>Targets of attacks that cross the circle boundary are immune to Charm, Fear, and Possession effects.</li>\n</ul>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Abjuration","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"TVLW3OLJe0O3VuCT"}
{"name":"Myssia's Minor Scrying","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Divination</h2><p><em>Having scouted out the bathhouse beforehand, you now focus in to hear the conversation happening hours later</em></p>\n<hr /><p>Choose a location you are familiar with. For the duration of the ritual, you can hear as if you were in that location. You can focus in on any sounds you hear, but you cannot move from the point you are sensing from. <em>(Still roll Arcana to determine interactions with any anti-divination magic)</em></p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Divination","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"nZxSRWIYlXjcD97A"}
{"name":"Shroud of Undeath","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Deception - Illusion</h2><p><em>Covers both the necro-radiance and olfactory spectrums</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you begin the ritual choose which type of corporeal undead the target will appear to be. For the duration of the ritual you or an ally appear to be that kind of undead for the purposes of the senses and any divination magic.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Deception - Illusion","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"YeS6patmr6HcDxTq"}
{"name":"Animal Messenger","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Communication</h2><p><em>You whisper a quick message to a nearby friend</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When beginning the ritual, choose a nearby animal that is not hostile to you. The animal approaches you, and you may give it a message up to 25 words in length.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-1-animal-messenger-animal-messenger-arcana-check\">Animal Messenger Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Distance</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>1 mile</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>5 miles</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>15 miles</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>30 miles</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>The animal will travel a maximum distance based on your Arcana check to a target you specify. You must physically describe the target, so you can say \"Give this message to one of the royal guards, whom wear heavy armor and have this specific emblem\" or you can give an exact description of an ally. The animal will then travel as quickly as possible to deliver your message to the target. If the animal does not make it to the target you are notified when it is stopped.</p>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Communication","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"Varies"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"n1KYAHCOuyFj68bp"}
{"name":"Clean","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Accommodation</h2><p><em>A spell to make Cinderella jealous</em></p>\n<hr /><p>This ritual completely cleans the contents of a room, dusting, polishing, and sweeping everything to \"Grandma Standard\". However, it won't rearrange furniture or make any other decisions related to arrangement that would actually make her happy.</p>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Accommodation","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"c5Z4bynrETyktgkW"}
{"name":"Detect Plants and Animals","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Divination</h2><p><em>As you complete the ritual your awareness grows, and you can feel the life force of non-sapient creatures around you.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you cast the ritual, specify a particular kind of animal or plant. Until the end of the duration, you can detect whether that particular kind of animal or plant is within a 5 times your Arcana check feet of you. Furthermore, you get a \"getting warmer\" or \"getting colder\" feeling for the nearest specimen of that plant or animal.</p>\n<p>As a standard action you may change what kind of animal or plant the ritual detects.</p>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Divination","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"byrKJ6lCeHNQSWIs"}
{"name":"Eyes of Alarm","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Abjuration</h2><p><em>You conjure forth a phantasmal sentry—a slender pillar 6 feet tall, topped with a floating, unblinking eye. The eye watches over your camp as you sleep and cries out an alert if danger approaches.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>This ritual creates watchful eyes that you place in any space within 50 feet of where you perform the ritual. Each eye is located in a particular square; it is intangible and can’t be interacted with physically. The eyes are nearly invisible and have a Stealth check result of 20 + your level to avoid detection.</p>\n<p>Your Arcana check determines how many eyes you can place and what type of vision or sensory ability they possess.</p>\n<h5 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-1-eyes-of-alarm-eyes-of-alarm-arcana-check\">Eyes of Alarm Arcana Check</h5>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Eyes Created</th>\n<th>Vision</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>One</td>\n<td>Normal</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>One</td>\n<td>Darkvision</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>Two</td>\n<td>Darkvision</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>Three</td>\n<td>Darkvision</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>The eyes do not hear, but they see well. Each uses your Perception modifier, with a +5 bonus.</p>\n<p>If an eye sees an intruder, it emits a loud warning sound defined by you during the ritual. This sound could be anything from a stentorian “Enemies approach!” to an owl’s screech to a fanfare of trumpets. The Perception DC to hear the eye’s sound is 0 (modified by distance as normal).</p>\n<p>The eyes never consider you an intruder. In addition, you can designate any number of other ritual participants as nonintruders. When you perform the ritual, you can also designate one or more categories of creatures that the eyes will ignore. You can define these categories by obvious physical characteristics (such as height, weight, or body shape), creature type (such as humanoid), creature race (such as hill giant), or obvious equipment (such as a creature carrying a shield with a flame emblazoned upon it).</p>\n<p>The ritual’s effects last for 24 hours or until you move more than 20 squares from all the eyes.</p>\n<p><strong>Optional Focus:</strong> You can extend the duration of this ritual indefinitely by using a focus of a small, jeweled eye made of silver and ruby, worth 100 gp. The ritual’s effects last as long as the focus remains within 100' of any of the eyes. You can hide or protect the ritual’s focus in any way you like, as long as it remains within 100' of the eyes</p>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Abjuration","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"15 minutes","duration":"10 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"jyBhDzPD64LMl7t3"}
{"name":"Identify","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Divination</h2><p><em>Concentrating on the item in front of you, you're able to gain insight on its properties and history.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You choose one object that you must touch throughout the casting of the ritual. If it is a magic item or some other magic-imbued object, you learn its properties and how to use them. You learn whether any spells are affecting the item and what they are. If the item was created by a spell, you learn which spell created it.</p>\n<p>As part of casting this ritual you may make an Arcana check to learn the history of the item.</p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:50%;\"><strong>Result</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;\"><strong>Effect</strong></td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;\">Failure</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;\">No history</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;\">Weak</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;\">Who crafted the item</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;\">Moderate</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;\">The most powerful owner</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;\">Strong</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;\">The most recent owner</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>If you instead touch a creature throughout the casting, you learn what spells, if any, are currently affecting it.</p>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Divination","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"NDDg4YQt2iUqpSzm"}
{"name":"Mask Smells","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Deception</h2><p><em>Grinding and igniting the components, you cover up an unpleasent or revealing odor</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You cover up any smells emanating from up to a 5' cube's worth of material for a duration based on your Arcana check. Depending on your result you may also be able to replace the smell with something more pleasing or otherwise desireable. You can always \"downgrade\" your new smell result.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-1-mask-smells-mask-smells-arcana-check\">Mask Smells Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Duration</th>\n<th>New Smell</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>1 hour</td>\n<td>Neutral</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>8 hours</td>\n<td>Vaguely Floral</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>48 hours</td>\n<td>Any weak smell</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>1 week</td>\n<td>Any strong smell</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Deception","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Varies"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"KXMK5T4gKbQHu8Rl"}
{"name":"Message","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Communication</h2><p><em>You whisper a message into a distant target's ear</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You send a one way message to a target creature you have met before or otherwise know and is also within 1 mile. Your Arcana check result determines the length of the message</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-1-message-message-arcana-check\">Message Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Length</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>10 words</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>25 words</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>75 words</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>200 words</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Communication","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"X2Kt97I5zWnxf3FH"}
{"name":"Speak with Animals","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 1 Environment</h2><p><em>It's amazing what the animals see but do not tell. Such as which way that talking llama went.</em></p>\n<hr /><div>For the ritual's duration you gain the ability to communicate with natural beasts. This does not make the animals friendly, nor does it let them know more than their experience and mobility would tell them.</div>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-1-speak-with-animals-speak-with-animals-arcana-check\">Speak with Animals Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Duration</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>One minute</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>Ten minutes</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>1 hour</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>8 hours</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"25 gp","category":"Level 1 Environment","componentCost":"5 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"Varies"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"aWPVnOAq6o5714tA"}
{"name":"Abundant Vegetation","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Environment</h2><p><em>The existing vegetation expands to impeding movement</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You can sculpt and empower the vegetation in an area, with the size based on your Arcana check result</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-2-abundant-vegetation-abundant-vegetation-arcana-check\">Abundant Vegetation Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Area</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>5' radius</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>15' radius</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>30' radius</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>60' radius</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>You can grow light vegetation into medium vegetation, which functions as difficult terrain. You can grow medium vegetation into heavy vegetation, which serves as blocking terrain. When you create blocking terrain you can choose whether it also obstructs vision.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Environment","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"jWEBPntqQmIdpeVv"}
{"name":"Darkness","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Travel</h2><p><em>The chosen area becomes utterly impermeable to light</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You create a sphere of utter blackness, the area determined by your Arcana check result</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-2-darkness-darkness-arcana-check\">Darkness Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Area</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>5' radius</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>15' radius</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>30' radius</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>60' radius</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>The darkness automatically overwhelms any magical light source with an Arcana check result lower than the Darkness. Natural darkvision does not allow a creature to see into the affected area.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Travel","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"30 minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"bUOAOdtC7KHSMNNf"}
{"name":"Darkvision","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Divination</h2><p><em>Your pupils dilate and become a swirling black vortex, pulling in the faintest amounts of light</em></p>\n<hr /><p>While you cast this ritual, choose yourself or an ally. The target gains the ability to see up to 60' through both nonmagical darkness and some forms of magical darkness based on your competing Arcana checks</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-2-darkvision-darkvision-arcana-check\">Darkvision Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Comparitive result</th>\n<th>Vision</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>5 or more</td>\n<td>See normally</td>\n</tr><tr><td>0 to 4</td>\n<td>Lightly obscured</td>\n</tr><tr><td>-5 to -1</td>\n<td>Heavily obscured</td>\n</tr><tr><td>-6 or less</td>\n<td>Can't see</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Divination","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"8 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"N1iLQnVs9NmiNXO7"}
{"name":"Detect Anima","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Divination</h2><p><em>Your vision deepens in intensity as you see the energy that flows through everything, clearly identifying the dark energies holding the skeletons together</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you cast the ritual, specify a particular kind of animate creature, such as a zombie or iron golem. Until the end of the duration, you can detect whether that particular kind of animate creature is within a 5 times your Arcana check feet of you. Furthermore, you get a \"getting warmer\" or \"getting colder\" feeling for the nearest specimen of that animate creature.</p>\n<p>As a standard action you may change what kind of animate creature the ritual detects.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Divination","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"qN5QMx8w6iakgXGV"}
{"name":"Hasal's Minor Senspr","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Divination</h2><p><em>The small, invisible node of magic placed in the King's Chamber allows you to hear his conversation with his scheming adviser later</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You place an invisible sensor in a location. This sensor can float in the air or stick to an object, moving with the object if the object moves. The duration of the sensor is based on your Arcana check result.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-2-hasals-minor-sensor-hasals-minor-sensor-arcana-check\">Hasal's Minor Sensor Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Duration</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>1 hour</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>8 hours</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>24 hours</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>72 hours</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>Wherever you are, you can listen into whatever the sensor is hearing as a free action. The sensor has normal hearing.</p>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Divination","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"5 minutes","duration":"Varies"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"LWSwG9BXEhsujKS3"}
{"name":"Talina's Lesser Detect Divination","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 2 Divination</h2><p><em>You sense if there's any active divination effects near you</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You scan a 60' radius for any active divination effects. The following effects are cumulative.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-2-talinas-lesser-detect-divination-talinas-lesser-detect-divination-arcana-check\">Talina's Lesser Detect Divination Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Effect</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9 or lower</td>\n<td>You learn if there is a divination effect</td>\n</tr><tr><td>10-13</td>\n<td>You learn where the divination effect is</td>\n</tr><tr><td>14-17</td>\n<td>You learn what the divination effect is</td>\n</tr><tr><td>18 or higher</td>\n<td>You learn who cast the divination effect</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"125 gp","category":"Level 2 Divination","componentCost":"25 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"hg1ZRXgzAgWm5fNn"}
{"name":"Create Climbing Holds","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Environment</h2><p><em>What was an insurmountable height is now an easy climb</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You transform a mostly vertical surface into one that's significantly easier to climb, adding convenient climbing holds that reduce the DC to climb the surface by 10. The size of the surface is determined by your Arcana check result</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-1-animal-messenger-animal-messenger-arcana-check\">Create Climbing Holds Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:99.8031%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th style=\"width:52.1654%;\">Result</th>\n<th style=\"width:47.6378%;\">Maximum Size</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:52.1654%;\">10 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width:47.6378%;\">25' by 5'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:52.1654%;\">11-14</td>\n<td style=\"width:47.6378%;\">50' by 10'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:52.1654%;\">15-18</td>\n<td style=\"width:47.6378%;\">100' by 15'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:52.1654%;\">19 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width:47.6378%;\">200' by 20'</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Environment","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"QE0mgoBAjOPktcTa"}
{"name":"Detect Humanoids","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Divination</h2><p><em>No goblin can hide from you</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you cast the ritual, specify a particular kind of humanoid, such as a human or an elf. Until the end of the duration, you can detect whether that particular kind of humanoid is within a 5 times your Arcana check feet of you. Furthermore, you get a \"getting warmer\" or \"getting colder\" feeling for the nearest specimen of that type of humanoid.</p>\n<p>As a standard action you may change what kind of humanoid the ritual detects. You may also broadly specify \"All humanoids\" to detect any humanoids near you.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Divination","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"KJS25nUCWniUnlDg"}
{"name":"Find Object","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Divination</h2><p><em>Now where is that sock...</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you use this ritual choose either a specific, individual object or a general type of object, either of which you must be familiar with. When you complete the ritual you learn where either the object is or the nearest example of that object based on your Arcana check. If you pick a general type of object you may designate specific objects you already know about to ignore for the \"nearest example\" result. If you pick a specific object and it has been broken into pieces you learn the location of the nearest piece, with the same \"designate already known pieces\" ability as with a general type of object.</p>\n<table style=\"width:99.8031%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th style=\"width:45.4724%;\">Result</th>\n<th style=\"width:54.3307%;\">Specificity</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">10 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">Abstract location (eg Sharn)</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">11-14</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">General location (eg The Cogs)</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">15-18</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">Specific location (Eg a specific building)</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">19 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">Exact location (Eg on top of a filing cabinet in a specific room)</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Divination","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"1 hour","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"AKeW16rNMsYLNARe"}
{"name":"Hasal's Lesser Sensor","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Divination</h2><p><em>Not for use in private locations without express permission</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You place an invisible sensor in a location. This sensor can float in the air or stick to an object, moving with the object if the object moves. The duration of the sensor is based on your Arcana check result.</p>\n<table style=\"width:99.8031%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th style=\"width:32.874%;\">Result</th>\n<th style=\"width:30.1181%;\">Duration</th>\n<th style=\"width:36.811%;\">Vision</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:32.874%;\">10 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width:30.1181%;\">1 hour</td>\n<td style=\"width:36.811%;\">Normal</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:32.874%;\">11-14</td>\n<td style=\"width:30.1181%;\">8 hours</td>\n<td style=\"width:36.811%;\">Low-light</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:32.874%;\">15-18</td>\n<td style=\"width:30.1181%;\">24 hours</td>\n<td style=\"width:36.811%;\">Darvision 30'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:32.874%;\">19 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width:30.1181%;\">72 hours</td>\n<td style=\"width:36.811%;\">Darkvision 60'</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>Wherever you are, you can see what the sensor is seeing as a free action. The sensor can see through magical darkness with an Arcana check lower than the one used for this ritual.</p>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Divination","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"5 minutes","duration":"Varies"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"Px5H9DMWP7fvlXuX"}
{"name":"Reshape Wood","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Environment</h2><p><em>You transform an ordinary block of wood into a duck.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You reshape a chunk of wood with size based on your Arcana check into any shape of your choice. You can discard material to be left aside but not create it.</p>\n<table style=\"width:99.8031%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th style=\"width:45.4724%;\">Result</th>\n<th style=\"width:54.3307%;\">Size</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">10 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">5' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">11-14</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">10' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">15-18</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">25' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">19 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">50' cube</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Environment","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"03wjcTxorMZVfLSB"}
{"name":"Silence","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 3 Deception</h2><p><em>A hush falls over the crowd.</em></p>\n<hr /><p>An area with a size based on your Arcana check result falls totally silent, preventing the use of Arcane, Divine, and Primal abilities in addition to preventing any ritual casting. Any creature inside the area is deafened and immune to Thunder damage.</p>\n<table style=\"width:99.8031%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th style=\"width:45.4724%;\">Result</th>\n<th style=\"width:54.3307%;\">Sphere radius</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">10 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">10'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">11-14</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">20'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">15-18</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">30'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:45.4724%;\">19 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width:54.3307%;\">50'</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"325 gp","category":"Level 3 Deception","componentCost":"65 gp","castingTime":"30 seconds","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"lb50oAXzgcLinNBl"}
{"name":"Analyze Portal","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Divination</h2><p><em>It's important to know whether a portal sends a target to the Demiplane of Extremely Painful Torture or the Semi-Elemental Plane of Ranch Dressing</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You analyze a magical portal, learning details based on your Arcana check result. What you learn is cumulutive - you learn what your result indicates and any information from lower check results.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-analyze-portal-analyze-portal-arcana-check\">Analyze Portal Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Details learned</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>10 or lower</td>\n<td>Whether the portal is one-way or two-way</td>\n</tr><tr><td>11-14</td>\n<td>Where the portal goes</td>\n</tr><tr><td>15-18</td>\n<td>Any restriction on the portal's functioning and a glimpse of the other side</td>\n</tr><tr><td>19 or higher</td>\n<td>Any special keywords or actions necessary to operate the portal</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Divination","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"8PSksgu9ooqIB4gt"}
{"name":"Animate Object","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Creation</h2><p><em>It takes a lot of casts to animate the entire kitchen</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You animate a number of objects based on your Arcana check result. Tiny objects count as half, large objects count as two, and huge objects count as four.</p>\n<h5 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-animate-object-animate-object-arcana-check\">Animate Object Arcana Check</h5>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Count</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>10 or lower</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr><tr><td>11-14</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr><tr><td>15-18</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr><tr><td>19 or higher</td>\n<td>8</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>The objects have statistics based on how much you expend on this ritual. You cannot cast this ritual at a level higher than your current level.</p>\n<h5 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-animate-object-animate-object-component-cost\">Animate Object Component Cost</h5>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Cost</th>\n<th>Level</th>\n<th>Damage</th>\n<th>HP</th>\n<th>AC</th>\n<th>Fort</th>\n<th>Ref</th>\n<th>Will</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>120 gp</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>2d6+4</td>\n<td>49</td>\n<td>16</td>\n<td>15</td>\n<td>12</td>\n<td>12</td>\n</tr><tr><td>440 gp</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>2d8+6</td>\n<td>70</td>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>14</td>\n<td>14</td>\n</tr><tr><td>1000 gp</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>3d6+9</td>\n<td>91</td>\n<td>19</td>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>15</td>\n<td>15</td>\n</tr><tr><td>65 ls</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>3d8+11</td>\n<td>112</td>\n<td>21</td>\n<td>20</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>17</td>\n</tr><tr><td>310 ls</td>\n<td>16</td>\n<td>4d8+11</td>\n<td>133</td>\n<td>22</td>\n<td>21</td>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>18</td>\n</tr><tr><td>785 ls</td>\n<td>19</td>\n<td>5d8+11</td>\n<td>154</td>\n<td>24</td>\n<td>23</td>\n<td>20</td>\n<td>20</td>\n</tr><tr><td>25 ad</td>\n<td>22</td>\n<td>5d8+15</td>\n<td>175</td>\n<td>25</td>\n<td>24</td>\n<td>21</td>\n<td>21</td>\n</tr><tr><td>205 ad</td>\n<td>25</td>\n<td>6d8+15</td>\n<td>196</td>\n<td>27</td>\n<td>26</td>\n<td>23</td>\n<td>23</td>\n</tr><tr><td>595 ad</td>\n<td>28</td>\n<td>7d8+15</td>\n<td>217</td>\n<td>28</td>\n<td>27</td>\n<td>24</td>\n<td>24</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>Objects have a melee basic attack with an attack bonus and damage value listed in the table. The damage type is at the DM's discretion based on the type of object, but in most cases will be bludgeoning.</p>\n<p>Tiny objects have half hit points and do half damage on a hit. Large objects have double hit points and can multiattack as a standard action, making two melee basic attacks. Huge objects have quadruple hit points, can multiattack as a standard action to make three melee basic attacks, and have 10' reach on their attacks.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Creation","componentCost":"Varies","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"7Q0OBsYlglqKmQJp"}
{"name":"Blindsight","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Divination</h2><p><em>Unnecessary for tracking Otyughs</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You give yourself or an ally the ability to sense their environment without the use of sight, dramatically boosting their auditory and olfactory senses. The range of the Blindsight depends on your Arcana check result.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-blindsight-blindsight-arcana-check\">Blindsight Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th style=\"width:87px;\">Result</th>\n<th style=\"width:130px;\">Blindsight range</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:87px;\">10 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width:130px;\">10'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:87px;\">11-14</td>\n<td style=\"width:130px;\">30'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:87px;\">15-18</td>\n<td style=\"width:130px;\">60'</td>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"width:87px;\">19 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width:130px;\">120'</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Divination","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"taaqvB6ZFghp7jRG"}
{"name":"Detect Immortals","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Divination</h2><p><em>Now where is that imp...</em></p>\n<hr /><p>When you cast the ritual, specify a particular kind of immortal, such as a demon or a type of devil. Until the end of the duration, you can detect whether that particular kind of immortal is within a 5 times your Arcana check feet of you. Furthermore, you get a \"getting warmer\" or \"getting colder\" feeling for the nearest specimen of that type of immortal.</p>\n<p>As a standard action you may change what kind of immortal the ritual detects. You may also broadly specify \"All immortals\" to detect any immortals near you.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Divination","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"1 minute","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"usPXCrS24Ef23VV0"}
{"name":"Elena's Conjuration: Water","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Creation</h2><p><em>Flash flood warning</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You conjure an amount of water based on your Arcana check result. When you begin casting the ritual designate where you want the water to appear, you must be within 100' and maintain line of sight for the duration of the ritual.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-elenas-conjuration-water-elenas-conjuration-water-arcana-check\">Elena's Conjuration: Water Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Total Volume</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>10 or lower</td>\n<td>1' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td>11-14</td>\n<td>5' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td>15-18</td>\n<td>10' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td>19 or higher</td>\n<td>20' cube</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Creation","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"1yx6u5Cask2qVxa3"}
{"name":"Hasal's Greater Sensor","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Divination</h2><p><em>Total AV surveillance</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You place an invisible sensor in a location. This sensor can float in the air or stick to an object, moving with the object if the object moves. The duration of the sensor is based on your Arcana check result.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-hasals-greater-sensor-hasals-greater-sensor-arcana-check\">Hasal's Greater Sensor Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Duration</th>\n<th>Vision</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>10 or lower</td>\n<td>8 hours</td>\n<td>Normal</td>\n</tr><tr><td>11-14</td>\n<td>24 hours</td>\n<td>Low-light</td>\n</tr><tr><td>15-18</td>\n<td>48 hours</td>\n<td>Darvision 30'</td>\n</tr><tr><td>19 or higher</td>\n<td>72 hours</td>\n<td>Darkvision 60'</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p>Wherever you are, you can see what the sensor is seeing and hear what the sensor is hearing as a free action. The sensor can see through magical darkness with an Arcana check lower than the one used for this ritual.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Divination","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"5 minutes","duration":"Varies"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"runVpVqqUvRguFGD"}
{"name":"Reshape Stone","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Creation</h2><p><em>Remove or create dams as needed</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You reshape a chunk of stone with size based on your Arcana check into any shape of your choice. You can discard material to be left aside but not create it.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-reshape-stone-reshape-stone-arcana-check\">Reshape Stone Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Size</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>10 or lower</td>\n<td>5' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td>11-14</td>\n<td>10' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td>15-18</td>\n<td>25' cube</td>\n</tr><tr><td>19 or higher</td>\n<td>50' cube</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Creation","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Instantaneous"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"lRdYFzPgyfAiXq1M"}
{"name":"Talina's Protection from Divination","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Abjuration</h2><p><em>For protecting and protection from evil plots</em></p>\n<hr /><p>As you cast this ritual you must hold an object that will be the focal point of the ritual. When you complete the ritual, an area based on your Arcana check result is protected from divination magic.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-talinas-protection-from-divination-talinas-protection-from-divination-arcana-check\">Talina's Protection from Divination Arcana Check</h4>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Area</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>10 or lower</td>\n<td>5' sphere</td>\n</tr><tr><td>11-14</td>\n<td>10' sphere</td>\n</tr><tr><td>15-18</td>\n<td>20' sphere</td>\n</tr><tr><td>19 or higher</td>\n<td>30' sphere</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Abjuration","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"24 hours"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"3hAwQ7DprwDrkB3U"}
{"name":"Whispering Word","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Communication</h2><p><em>Imagine what kind messages people would share if long distance instantaneous communication were common</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You send a message or sound on the wind to a designated spot. The whispering wind travels to a specific location within range that is familiar to you, provided that it can find a way to the location. A whispering wind is as gentle and unnoticed as a zephyr until it reaches the location. It then delivers its whisper-quiet message or other sound. Note that the message is delivered regardless of whether anyone is present to hear it. The wind then dissipates.</p>\n<p>Your Arcana check result determines how many rounds the ritual lasts. Each round the ritual can speak up to 25 words, make other sounds, or simply be the faint stirring of the air. You can likewise cause the whispering wind to move as slowly as 1 mile per hour or as quickly as 1 mile per 10 minutes.</p>\n<h5 id=\"rituals-heroic-tier-rituals-level-4-whispering-wind-whispering-wind-arcana-check\">Whispering Wind Arcana Check</h5>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Result</th>\n<th>Duration</th>\n<th>Max range</th>\n</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>10 or lower</td>\n<td>1 round</td>\n<td>5 miles</td>\n</tr><tr><td>11-14</td>\n<td>2 rounds</td>\n<td>10 miles</td>\n</tr><tr><td>15-18</td>\n<td>4 rounds</td>\n<td>20 miles</td>\n</tr><tr><td>19 or higher</td>\n<td>12 rounds</td>\n<td>40 miles</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Communication","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"10 minutes","duration":"Varies"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"J2defRz1gYzECkjF"}
{"name":"Zone of Truth","permission":{"default":0,"DXmL7wc74NRmbZdk":3},"type":"ritual","data":{"description":"<h2>Level 4 Divination</h2><p><em>Finishing the circle around your captive, you step back and ask \"Who killed the Duchess?\"</em></p>\n<hr /><p>You create a magical zone that guards against deception in a 15-foot-circle. Until the ritual ends, a creature that enters the ritual's area for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there must make an Charisma check against your Arcana check result. On a failed check, a creature can't speak a deliberate lie while in the radius. You know whether each creature succeeds or fails on its saving throw.</p>\n<p>An affected creature is aware of the ritual and can thus avoid answering questions to which it would normally respond with a lie. Such creatures can be evasive in its answers as long as it remains within the boundaries of the truth.</p>","marketPrice":"600 gp","category":"Level 4 Divination","componentCost":"120 gp","castingTime":"15 minutes","duration":"1 hour"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"zm46nh7yWa5BFQCH"}
